title: Great Jetspectations
description:
Mina and Mike Golic, Jr. field an array of questions from listeners including- whether or not Matt Ryan can get back to the Super Bowl with Indy, why Detroit might be too good to get a top 5 pick next year, a position group by position group breakdown of the Chiefs and Bills, favorite TV show characters, and the WR that would be the most fun to go to Disney World with.
